{"tid":1488054,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[學生哥同我入嚟] 5分鐘填份問卷 攞M記現金卷","createTime":"2019-08-19T13:38:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T13:50:23.000Z","uid":292805,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cbdbe3142c6949ff5bdd99971894dffe4a765cd1","tid":1488054,"uid":292805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:38:42.000Z","msg":"你地而家發夢發到冇錢食飯，我見到咁好心酸呀！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁啱有朋友share咗份問卷嚟，填完就有$20 M記現金卷，雖然數目唔多，但起碼都叫做 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">幫到下班冇錢開飯既學生</span></span>，反正冇成本，入嚟填填呀！<br />\n<br />\n就算唔係學生既巴打，入嚟幫手填填，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">攞完個現金卷，捐比物資站都好呀！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家仲有咩渠道可以幫到班學生，都不妨share出嚟啦，麻煩哂巴打們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問卷網係呢到！<br />\n<a href=\"http://forms.gle/JngPCr4znhDNMd4b9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FJngPCr4znhDNMd4b9&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NACUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=7cba0dba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">forms.gle/JngPCr4znhDNMd4b9</a>"},{"pid":"d965d8ecbcfd4116640f6b3687c91e64bcfb7d9e","tid":1488054,"uid":175159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:41:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6E2wt3h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6E2wt3h.jpg&h=62131472&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gYGk6PY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgYGk6PY.jpg&h=5869b84f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f5zCpBD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff5zCpBD.jpg&h=11da5a0e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx